    "_postman_id": "8d7a01b8-0b54-4b0f-8a52-79e3d6f2b3d1",
    "name": "Tike API",
    "description": "Tike API with OAuth2 authentication and API Key security.\n\n**Authentication:**\n- All endpoints (except /health) require an API Key via `X-API-Key` header\n- Protected endpoints also require OAuth Bearer token via `Authorization` header\n\n**Development API Key:**\n- Set `{{api_key}}` in environment to: `dev_test_ddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddd`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
